<div class="final-text p-2 mt-8">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">BTTS au GG/NG ni Nini?</h2>
    <p>Hapa tunatabiri iwapo timu zote zitafungana au vinginevyo</p>
    <ul>
        <li>
            <b>GG au YES</b> ina maananisha timu zote kufungana. Mfano wa matokeo sahihi ya chaguo hili ni: 1:1, 2:1, 1:2, 3:1, 3:2, 2:2, n.k.
        </li>
        <br>
        <li>
            <b>NG au NO</b> inamaanisha timu moja au zote zisifungane. Mfano wa matokeo sahihi ya chaguo hili ni: 0:0, 0:1, 1:0, 2:0, 3:0, 0:2, 0:3, n.k
        </li>
      </ul>
</div>

<script is:inline>

    // Add click handlers
    ["jana", "leo", "kesho"].forEach((day) => {
        document.getElementById(`btts-btn-${day}`).addEventListener("click", () => {
            // Hide all tables
            ["jana", "leo", "kesho"].forEach((d) => {
                document.getElementById(`btts-table-${d}`).classList.add('hidden')
                document.getElementById(`btts-btn-${d}`).classList.remove("border", "border-secondary");
            });

            // Show selected table and highlight button
            document.getElementById(`btts-table-${day}`).classList.remove('hidden');
            document.getElementById(`btts-btn-${day}`).classList.add("border", "border-secondary");
        });
    });
</script>